1
00:00:05,659 --> 00:00:08,355
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,429 --> 00:00:12,297
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,366 --> 00:00:16,359
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,704 --> 00:00:19,195
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,273 --> 00:00:23,334
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,411 --> 00:00:27,370
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,849 --> 00:00:33,582
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,288 --> 00:00:37,257
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,693 --> 00:00:41,786
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,530 --> 00:00:43,827
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,165 --> 00:00:46,725
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,775 --> 00:01:00,145
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,347 --> 00:01:01,507
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,582 --> 00:01:05,382
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:10,918
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,192 --> 00:01:12,523
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,593 --> 00:01:13,992
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,061 --> 00:01:20,330
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:30,306 --> 00:01:32,206
Sakura Haruno vs. Ino Yamanaka

20
00:01:34,414 --> 00:01:35,711
At this point in time,

21
00:01:38,118 --> 00:01:40,746
I don't even plan to fight
over Sasuke with you.

22
00:01:41,721 --> 00:01:42,688
Sakura!

23
00:01:42,956 --> 00:01:45,754
Do you know who
you're lipping off to?!

24
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:49,185
Don't press your luck,
crybaby Sakura!

25
00:01:49,396 --> 00:01:53,799
It seems like...
it seems like Sakura was out of line!

26
00:01:53,867 --> 00:01:57,166
Ino's eyes show incredible anger.
She's scary.

27
00:01:57,470 --> 00:01:58,869
Hmm.

28
00:01:59,606 --> 00:02:00,504
That's not it...

29
00:02:00,574 --> 00:02:01,063
Huh?

30
00:02:01,808 --> 00:02:04,276
Sakura's not the kind of kid
to do things

31
00:02:04,344 --> 00:02:07,074
like needlessly flaunt her
own power and hurt people.

32
00:02:08,215 --> 00:02:12,151
She doesn't like having Ino
taking pity on her and pulling punches.

33
00:02:31,404 --> 00:02:32,462
- <i>This time for sure,</i>
- <i>This time for sure,</i>

34
00:02:34,074 --> 00:02:35,132
- <i>with full strength,</i>
- <i>with full strength,</i>

35
00:02:37,744 --> 00:02:41,271
- <i>a fair... fight!</i>
- <i>a fair... fight!</i>

36
00:02:42,215 --> 00:02:47,949
The Ultimate Battle: Cha!

37
00:03:04,037 --> 00:03:05,800
<i>Just a Clone Jutsu?!</i>

38
00:03:06,439 --> 00:03:09,033
This isn't a Ninja Academy's
graduation exam!

39
00:03:09,476 --> 00:03:11,273
You think you can beat me...

40
00:03:11,344 --> 00:03:13,209
with a textbook ninja art?!

41
00:03:14,648 --> 00:03:17,412
<i>If I look carefully, I can find out,</i>
<i>which is the real one right away...</i>

42
00:03:17,751 --> 00:03:20,219
<i>Chakra to my feet at a burst... Then...</i>

43
00:03:20,453 --> 00:03:21,579
<i>repel off the ground!</i>

44
00:03:21,855 --> 00:03:22,378
<i>Fast!</i>

45
00:03:29,362 --> 00:03:31,728
If you think I'm the crybaby Sakura
I was until recently,

46
00:03:31,798 --> 00:03:33,129
you'll get your fingers burned!

47
00:03:34,467 --> 00:03:36,230
Come like you mean it, Ino!

48
00:03:39,205 --> 00:03:41,867
I appreciate you saying that...

49
00:03:42,942 --> 00:03:45,502
I'll go like I mean it, as you wish!

50
00:03:52,986 --> 00:03:54,783
Way to go Sakura!

51
00:03:54,988 --> 00:03:55,886
Great!

52
00:03:55,955 --> 00:03:57,388
Really great!

53
00:03:57,824 --> 00:03:59,689
With the fundamental movements
using Chakra,

54
00:03:59,826 --> 00:04:01,487
she's topnotch among the rookies...

55
00:04:01,695 --> 00:04:02,354
Huh?

56
00:04:02,429 --> 00:04:04,727
Sakura is at her best.

57
00:04:05,198 --> 00:04:08,258
That means...
Is she better than me?

58
00:04:08,668 --> 00:04:09,293
Well!

59
00:04:09,502 --> 00:04:10,332
That's right.

60
00:04:10,603 --> 00:04:11,900
Awww

61
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:15,837
Sending,"Chakra all throughout
the body and

62
00:04:15,975 --> 00:04:18,409
using the technique
with it at a right timing...

63
00:04:19,112 --> 00:04:21,603
Those techniques alone
are better than Sasuke.

64
00:04:22,849 --> 00:04:24,976
Well, from the start,
she was extremely good at...

65
00:04:25,051 --> 00:04:28,748
controlling her Chakra, so...

66
00:04:30,657 --> 00:04:32,818
<i>Magnificent movements, Sakura!</i>

67
00:04:43,937 --> 00:04:46,201
<i>However, her opponent is good too.</i>

68
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:49,107
<i>This evenly matched battle</i>
<i>looks to take awhile!</i>

69
00:04:58,184 --> 00:05:01,085
<i>Since when did this girl</i>
<i>get this strong?!</i>

70
00:05:02,522 --> 00:05:05,252
<i>I can make it, too!</i>

71
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,818
You little!

72
00:05:15,001 --> 00:05:16,127
Whoa!

73
00:05:18,438 --> 00:05:20,201
<i>At this rate, it'll never end.</i>

74
00:05:23,009 --> 00:05:24,101
<i>This is long...</i>

75
00:05:25,578 --> 00:05:27,136
<i>They've been going at it</i>
<i>for ten minutes, at the least.</i>

76
00:05:37,824 --> 00:05:41,419
You shouldn't be evenly
matched with me!

77
00:05:42,962 --> 00:05:46,864
What makes you think
I'm evenly matched with you...

78
00:05:47,100 --> 00:05:49,694
who's only concerned with looks
and growing your hair frivolously?!

79
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,802
You!

80
00:05:55,208 --> 00:05:57,301
You carry your mocking
of me too far!

81
00:05:57,777 --> 00:05:58,607
Idiot.

82
00:05:58,812 --> 00:06:00,677
She's going for the bait.

83
00:06:01,314 --> 00:06:04,283
Who knows what Ino will do!

84
00:06:04,617 --> 00:06:07,279
I don't like Ino when she's that way!

85
00:06:26,172 --> 00:06:27,503
You're simple minded...

86
00:06:28,475 --> 00:06:29,533
<i>Uh oh.</i>

87
00:06:30,276 --> 00:06:31,766
<i>She's totally lost it!</i>

88
00:06:36,216 --> 00:06:37,376
I don't need this!

89
00:06:43,957 --> 00:06:46,118
S-Scary...

90
00:06:46,926 --> 00:06:48,655
I'll put an end to this right now!

91
00:06:49,596 --> 00:06:52,895
I'll make you say that you lost!

92
00:06:53,333 --> 00:06:55,995
Hey, don't tell me...

93
00:06:56,336 --> 00:06:57,530
Could it be?

94
00:07:01,474 --> 00:07:03,032
<i>As I recall, that Sign is...</i>

95
00:07:03,476 --> 00:07:04,704
I knew it...

96
00:07:05,378 --> 00:07:07,346
She's planning to do
the Mind Transfer Jutsu!

97
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:09,941
Man... That idiot!

98
00:07:12,252 --> 00:07:16,313
I understand your feelings of frustration,
but that's futile.

99
00:07:16,756 --> 00:07:17,415
Humph!

100
00:07:17,891 --> 00:07:19,358
I wonder!

101
00:07:19,926 --> 00:07:22,394
Ninja Art, Mind Transfer Jutsu...

102
00:07:23,062 --> 00:07:26,862
A Jutsu where the user can take
over the opponent's spirit

103
00:07:26,933 --> 00:07:29,094
and wrest their body away
for a few minutes...

104
00:07:29,168 --> 00:07:31,830
by discharging all of
their own spiritual energy

105
00:07:31,905 --> 00:07:34,203
and striking the enemy with it.

106
00:07:35,074 --> 00:07:39,807
But, there are major flaws
to this formidable Jutsu.

107
00:07:40,713 --> 00:07:48,950
First, the discharged spiritual energy
can only fly straight and at a slow speed.

108
00:07:49,856 --> 00:07:56,352
Second, even in the case of failing
to hit the enemy and missing,

109
00:07:56,496 --> 00:07:58,964
the user can't return to her
own body for several minutes.

110
00:08:00,099 --> 00:08:03,068
I should add that during
that interval, the user's,

111
00:08:03,136 --> 00:08:07,937
in other words, your main body
will turn into a doll that won't move at all!

112
00:08:09,242 --> 00:08:09,936
<i>In the first place,</i>

113
00:08:10,009 --> 00:08:13,809
<i>the Mind Transfer Jutsu is used</i>
<i>for spying and is not a Jutsu for battle.</i>

114
00:08:14,847 --> 00:08:19,841
<i>Ino, using that Jutsu here</i>
<i>would be equal to suicide...</i>

115
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:23,281
<i>It shouldn't be particularly</i>
<i>scary if she moves about...</i>

116
00:08:24,090 --> 00:08:26,581
<i>And not only that,</i>
<i>if she dodges the Jutsu,</i>

117
00:08:26,659 --> 00:08:28,923
<i>she can beat the heck out</i>
<i>of the non moving opponent.</i>

118
00:08:30,229 --> 00:08:34,131
<i>If that happens, Hayate will be forced</i>
<i>to put an end to the match...</i>

119
00:08:35,101 --> 00:08:36,534
So what?!

120
00:08:36,869 --> 00:08:38,894
I won't know unless I try!

121
00:08:40,373 --> 00:08:41,806
If you miss, it's over.

122
00:08:42,075 --> 00:08:44,839
You know that, right?

123
00:08:45,945 --> 00:08:49,642
<i>In the first place,</i>
<i>it's a combination Jutsu to be used</i>

124
00:08:49,716 --> 00:08:51,911
<i>after stopping the opponent's</i>
<i>movements during a battle</i>

125
00:08:51,985 --> 00:08:53,145
<i>with my Shadow Possession Jutsu.</i>

126
00:08:53,453 --> 00:08:54,852
<i>There's no way!</i>

127
00:08:55,788 --> 00:08:57,187
<i>There is no way, it will hit...</i>

128
00:09:04,163 --> 00:09:05,095
Idiot! Stop!

129
00:09:05,431 --> 00:09:08,059
Ninja Art, Mind Transfer Jutsu!

130
00:09:22,649 --> 00:09:23,707
Which one?

131
00:09:31,958 --> 00:09:33,653
That was unfortunate...

132
00:09:36,729 --> 00:09:37,559
Ino.

133
00:09:38,431 --> 00:09:40,023
Has the fat lady sung?

134
00:09:40,366 --> 00:09:41,765
She went and did it...

135
00:09:44,037 --> 00:09:45,561
Then, it's over, eh.

136
00:09:51,244 --> 00:09:52,006
This is?!

137
00:09:55,081 --> 00:09:57,413
You fell for it, Sakura!

138
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:01,546
I finally caught you!

139
00:10:03,489 --> 00:10:04,478
It can't be!

140
00:10:06,793 --> 00:10:07,953
Yes, it can.

141
00:10:09,028 --> 00:10:12,259
My Sign weaving earlier was just an act,

142
00:10:13,066 --> 00:10:16,934
to drive you who was running
about into this contrivance.

143
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:18,534
So?

144
00:10:19,072 --> 00:10:20,835
You can't move at all, can you?

145
00:10:21,674 --> 00:10:25,474
It's special rope that's my hair
with Chakra poured in!

146
00:10:28,347 --> 00:10:32,909
With this, it will be over when
I enter your body and say "give up!"

147
00:10:35,021 --> 00:10:37,956
It wouldn't miss
a hundred percent of the time!

148
00:10:38,591 --> 00:10:39,990
<i>I see...</i>

149
00:10:40,893 --> 00:10:44,420
That idiot... Her losing it
was also an act?

150
00:10:44,864 --> 00:10:46,525
Get out of there, Sakura!

151
00:10:48,067 --> 00:10:48,863
<i>I can't move!</i>

152
00:10:50,002 --> 00:10:50,627
Then...

153
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,760
Mind Transfer Jutsu!

154
00:11:17,430 --> 00:11:19,159
That was unfortunate...

155
00:11:20,666 --> 00:11:21,860
She missed!

156
00:11:23,636 --> 00:11:24,466
No!

157
00:11:25,037 --> 00:11:25,833
Sakura...

158
00:11:26,305 --> 00:11:27,363
Sakura!

159
00:11:30,076 --> 00:11:31,008
Sakura!

160
00:11:50,782 --> 00:11:53,410
W-What's with Ino?

161
00:11:53,819 --> 00:11:58,188
Also... Sakura's acting kind of strange!
Believe it!

162
00:11:59,091 --> 00:12:00,490
But... surely this is her chance!

163
00:12:00,826 --> 00:12:03,226
Do it, Sakura!

164
00:12:04,496 --> 00:12:05,428
<i>It's no use.</i>

165
00:12:06,231 --> 00:12:08,529
To think, the Mind Transfer Jutsu there...

166
00:12:09,234 --> 00:12:10,223
Sakura's had it.

167
00:12:11,970 --> 00:12:12,834
Mind Transfer?!

168
00:12:13,872 --> 00:12:16,397
That means Sakura right now is...

169
00:12:18,043 --> 00:12:18,907
Yes.

170
00:12:19,778 --> 00:12:22,906
Sakura's spirit has been
completely taken over by Ino.

171
00:12:23,682 --> 00:12:24,444
What?!

172
00:12:25,917 --> 00:12:28,442
Ino is inside of Sakura's body now!

173
00:12:29,221 --> 00:12:29,880
Well.

174
00:12:30,255 --> 00:12:32,519
Ino's purpose is most likely...

175
00:12:35,060 --> 00:12:36,493
<i>With this, it's over.</i>

176
00:12:37,796 --> 00:12:39,696
<i>Good bye, Sakura...</i>

177
00:12:51,977 --> 00:12:55,845
I... Sakura Haruno concede...

178
00:12:57,149 --> 00:12:58,707
- this match...
- No!

179
00:12:59,451 --> 00:13:00,850
Sakura!

180
00:13:02,087 --> 00:13:02,746
Tsk!

181
00:13:03,288 --> 00:13:05,222
He's annoying

182
00:13:05,690 --> 00:13:07,749
You did your hardest to get here!

183
00:13:07,893 --> 00:13:11,488
You'll disgrace women if you lose
to that Sasuke-obsessed girl!

184
00:13:12,898 --> 00:13:15,423
Like I said, those words
are useless...

185
00:13:19,471 --> 00:13:20,199
<i>What's...</i>

186
00:13:25,911 --> 00:13:27,003
<i>this bad chill?!</i>

187
00:13:31,883 --> 00:13:34,010
<i>Naruto is annoying!</i>

188
00:13:38,523 --> 00:13:42,220
<i>Anyway, that's right...</i>
<i>not to Ino I won't...</i>

189
00:13:43,261 --> 00:13:44,285
Sakura?!

190
00:13:45,330 --> 00:13:46,490
This can't be happening...

191
00:13:50,001 --> 00:13:51,059
What's the matter?

192
00:13:52,504 --> 00:13:53,368
Are you conceding?

193
00:13:57,042 --> 00:13:58,839
I won't be conceding!

194
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:00,605
No Way!

195
00:14:01,713 --> 00:14:03,305
Cha!

196
00:14:05,617 --> 00:14:06,811
<i>Which is it?</i>

197
00:14:07,719 --> 00:14:09,880
W-What's going on?!

198
00:14:10,622 --> 00:14:11,281
<i>Sakura?!</i>

199
00:14:12,324 --> 00:14:13,313
No way!

200
00:14:17,128 --> 00:14:19,119
I messed up my Jutsu?

201
00:14:19,631 --> 00:14:25,661
Ino... You'll have a terrible time of it
if you don't get out of me quick!

202
00:14:29,074 --> 00:14:31,133
What's wrong, with Ino?

203
00:14:36,047 --> 00:14:40,381
<i>No... I won't hold on at this rate...</i>

204
00:14:41,586 --> 00:14:42,280
Release!

205
00:15:02,073 --> 00:15:05,941
<i>It can't be...</i>
<i>She shattered Ino's Jutsu!</i>

206
00:15:06,845 --> 00:15:09,575
<i>She used too much energy</i>
<i>before the Jutsu...</i>

207
00:15:10,915 --> 00:15:12,940
<i>So she didn't have enough Chakra?!</i>

208
00:15:17,756 --> 00:15:22,318
To think she has two spirits...
What are you?!

209
00:15:26,197 --> 00:15:28,665
Strength that ranks with beauty.

210
00:15:29,501 --> 00:15:32,959
Girls can't survive if they're not tough!

211
00:15:33,905 --> 00:15:35,497
<i>If caught in that spell,</i>

212
00:15:36,107 --> 00:15:38,769
<i>it's not that easy to cast out</i>
<i>the invader...</i>

213
00:15:40,412 --> 00:15:41,902
<i>Ino's lack of Chakra...</i>

214
00:15:42,647 --> 00:15:43,705
<i>There's also that...</i>

215
00:15:44,516 --> 00:15:46,245
<i>But what was more effective</i>
<i>than that...</i>

216
00:15:46,851 --> 00:15:51,083
<i>was the combative spirit towards</i>
<i>Ino she has inside her heart.</i>

217
00:15:51,856 --> 00:15:57,817
<i>So that was awakened with Naruto's voice</i>
<i>as the trigger and she cast Ino out?</i>

218
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:00,429
<i>There's nothing to it.</i>

219
00:16:00,832 --> 00:16:02,197
<i>Like Naruto...</i>

220
00:16:02,534 --> 00:16:06,527
<i>Sakura's fighting spirit was</i>
<i>much stronger than others.</i>

221
00:16:07,072 --> 00:16:07,970
- This is!
- This is!

222
00:16:09,474 --> 00:16:14,207
<i>But, both of them should</i>
<i>have hardly any Chakra left.</i>

223
00:16:18,516 --> 00:16:19,574
- <i>This</i> is...
- <i>This</i> is...

224
00:16:19,818 --> 00:16:20,614
- <i>the end!</i>
- <i>the end!</i>

225
00:17:30,388 --> 00:17:32,822
Both parties are unable
to continue the match!

226
00:17:33,691 --> 00:17:35,283
By double knockout,

227
00:17:35,593 --> 00:17:38,721
no one gets through the
fourth battle of the preliminary!

228
00:17:39,831 --> 00:17:40,729
- What?!
- Huh?!

229
00:17:44,436 --> 00:17:45,494
Now then...

230
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:47,196
Good grief.

231
00:17:49,207 --> 00:17:50,606
Hey, Ino!

232
00:17:50,875 --> 00:17:51,807
Sakura!

233
00:17:51,876 --> 00:17:53,104
Sakura!

234
00:17:53,278 --> 00:17:55,439
A-A-Are you okay?!

235
00:18:07,559 --> 00:18:09,618
Treatment's not necessary.

236
00:18:10,695 --> 00:18:13,061
They'll probably wake up after awhile.

237
00:18:17,869 --> 00:18:20,633
But, that was surprising...

238
00:18:21,639 --> 00:18:22,606
Yeah...

239
00:18:23,975 --> 00:18:25,738
Naruto and Sasuke aside...

240
00:18:26,511 --> 00:18:30,311
to think even that Sakura who didn't
have what it took has grown this much...

241
00:18:32,851 --> 00:18:34,375
<i>A lot happened,</i>

242
00:18:34,886 --> 00:18:37,650
<i>but I really feel like it</i>
<i>was a good thing...</i>

243
00:18:39,224 --> 00:18:40,885
<i>sending her to this Chunin Exam.</i>

244
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:52,600
Tenten vs. Temari

245
00:18:56,207 --> 00:18:59,665
<i>Seeing that made me all fired up, too!</i>

246
00:19:01,212 --> 00:19:01,974
Now...

247
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:04,304
The second one from the
Land of Sand, huh...

248
00:19:04,883 --> 00:19:07,408
- This looks to be an interesting match.
- Do your best, Tenten!

249
00:19:16,227 --> 00:19:19,754
It looks like you finally
woke up, eh... Sakura.

250
00:19:21,432 --> 00:19:22,057
Huh?!

251
00:19:22,133 --> 00:19:25,159
Tenten, power of youth!

252
00:19:25,436 --> 00:19:26,368
Go-Go!

253
00:19:26,437 --> 00:19:28,667
There is no limit to your youth!

254
00:19:29,574 --> 00:19:32,338
Our match is already over.

255
00:19:37,582 --> 00:19:40,745
Did I... lose?

256
00:19:44,889 --> 00:19:47,119
I'm the one who wants to cry...

257
00:19:48,159 --> 00:19:50,855
To think I tied with somebody like you...

258
00:19:52,230 --> 00:19:52,889
Huh?

259
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:55,224
Here!

260
00:19:58,570 --> 00:20:00,800
You also got a flower to bloom, didn't you?

261
00:20:01,506 --> 00:20:02,939
A beautiful flower!

262
00:20:09,814 --> 00:20:10,473
Ino...

263
00:20:20,658 --> 00:20:21,625
However...

264
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,022
the next time we fight,

265
00:20:24,095 --> 00:20:26,063
it won't end with you
getting knocked out!

266
00:20:26,631 --> 00:20:27,222
Hm?!

267
00:20:28,099 --> 00:20:32,536
And... I won't hand over
Sasuke to you!

268
00:20:34,272 --> 00:20:37,503
I return the same line to you!

269
00:20:40,111 --> 00:20:40,941
- Humph!
- Humph!

270
00:20:42,914 --> 00:20:44,347
The fifth battle...

271
00:20:44,849 --> 00:20:48,615
Tenten, Temari...
come forward!

272
00:21:05,732 --> 00:21:10,192
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

273
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:18,678
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

274
00:21:19,613 --> 00:21:28,351
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

275
00:21:28,722 --> 00:21:36,595
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

276
00:21:37,864 --> 00:21:43,530
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

277
00:21:43,603 --> 00:21:47,369
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

278
00:21:47,441 --> 00:21:51,002
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

279
00:21:51,344 --> 00:21:59,877
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

280
00:22:00,153 --> 00:22:05,352
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

281
00:22:05,425 --> 00:22:09,828
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

282
00:22:09,896 --> 00:22:13,662
<i>Just sing.</i>

283
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:19,065
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

284
00:22:19,139 --> 00:22:21,334
<i>The two are one</i>

285
00:22:21,441 --> 00:22:27,710
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

286
00:22:28,215 --> 00:22:33,312
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

287
00:22:36,887 --> 00:22:38,354
You know! You know!

288
00:22:38,422 --> 00:22:40,617
I feel like women battles
are incredible, or...

289
00:22:41,592 --> 00:22:43,287
Women are scary.

290
00:22:43,527 --> 00:22:44,050
Huh?

291
00:22:44,228 --> 00:22:45,058
Hey-hey!

292
00:22:45,229 --> 00:22:47,129
This isn't the time to be
withdrawing, Shikamaru.

293
00:22:47,498 --> 00:22:51,525
You're kind of a plain, or a lousy,
or an unimpressive guy, aren't you?

294
00:22:51,869 --> 00:22:55,032
If you don't really put your whole heart
into it, things will get hairy for you.

295
00:22:55,673 --> 00:23:00,133
Next episode:
"Killer Kunoichi and a Shaky Shikamaru"

296
00:23:00,644 --> 00:23:03,044
This is really, seriously bad!
